item.description:
Sun elven opinions on races outside of the Tel-quessir were far more strained. Sun elves could be incredibly prejudiced, to the point of some even refusing to aid a dying human if it mildly inconvenienced them. Many sun elves objected to speaking in any language other than Elven or even to speaking with members of other races at all. These prejudices were partially rooted in past wrongs done by humans unto sun elves, though in truth they often only served to heighten present tensions.

item.description:
You are obsessed with spiders. They fi ll your dreams and your
waking thoughts. The extent of your preoccupation does not
stop with ordinary spiders: You are fascinated by all spider-
kind, from the monstrous spiders of the Underdark to the
dreaded bebiliths that the priestesses conjure for the most
profane rituals.
Even when not studying spiders, you fi nd ways to bring
them up in conversation, dropping fascinating (to you) tid-
bits and trivia about different
breeds of spiders, their mating
habits, and their hunting
habits, and going to great
lengths to extol the virtues
of vermin.

item.dc:creator: Damafaud
item.description:
279

Mother

“Mommy knows the best.”
Neutral Support

Mother’s Love (Passive) - Your child is [player]. If your child is going to die in any way, you will instead protect him. Your child and your alignment will turn into Neutral Killer.
Silly Boy (Passive) - You will share a chat with your child. You will visit any player he does. If investigated, your alignment will be that of your child. Any empowerment or frame that affects your child will affect you.

Momma Will Protect You (Day) [Neutral Killer] - Kill someone. This can only be done when someone is on the stand. - Infinite uses. 2 days cooldown.

MY BABY! (Night) - Tonight, you will attack anyone that visits your child. - 3 uses
Story Time (Night) - Teach your child a passive, day, or night actions from SFoL Grand Idea Class Thread V2. Only actions with infinite uses can be taught. Your child cannot have more than 2 passives, 2 day actions, and 2 night actions. New actions will replace old one. [Infinite moves]

Your objective is to protect your child from any harm.
